  m_text: "Sometimes the simplest words carry the most meaning. \u201CHello world\u201D
    has always been the first step into something new, a small signal of creation,
    curiosity, and growth. Even though this one is missing a letter, it reminds me
    that imperfection is part of the journey. Progress is built not on flawless starts
    but on the courage to begin, adjust, and keep moving forward."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
